### login local (requiere email verificado)
POST http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mail": "juan1.perez@example.com",
  "password": "ClaveSegura123!"
}

### login Google
POST http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/auth/google
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idToken": "GOOGLE_ID_TOKEN"
}

### verificar email local
POST http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/auth/verify-email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "TOKEN_RECIBIDO_POR_MAIL"
}

### obtener usuario autenticado
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
